snippet.title: The Startup Vlog || 10k subscribers!
snippet.description:
10k Subscribers || the startup vlog

ANNOUNCEMENT TIME STAMP: 10:06

This one is a bit of a different one since I didn't get a lot done the last two weeks so I didn't really have anything new to show. So this is more of just my life in the last two weeks and also a huge thank you to you for subscribing to this channel. It means a lot! 

And in next weeks video I will build an app from start to finish and publish it so that you can download it and use it if you feel like it :)

Hope you enjoy this video that is a bit different from my regular startup vlog!
